{"ja224:0.1":"Jataka ","ja224:0.2":"Dukanipata ","ja224:0.3":"Kasavavagga ","ja224:0.4":"4. Kumbhilajataka ","ja224:1.1":"“Yassete caturo dhamma, ","ja224:1.2":"vanarinda yatha tava; ","ja224:1.3":"Saccam dhammo dhiti cago, ","ja224:1.4":"dittham so ativattati. ","ja224:2.1":"Yassa cete na vijjanti, ","ja224:2.2":"guna paramabhaddaka; ","ja224:2.3":"Saccam dhammo dhiti cago, ","ja224:2.4":"dittham so nativattati”ti. ","ja224:3.1":"Kumbhilajatakam catuttham. "}